{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC03_LIN_730.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x26,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "I wonder what happened to the other Linca..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Now that I think about it,<CR>I still don't know that much about it.<CR>But I don't wanna be too nosy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I wonder what the other Linca's real name is..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm, you can call me Linca, as well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x125,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Whaaa‐!? Sh-Sh-She's here!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x19c,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Okay, don't cause a commotion now. I don't wanna call attention to myself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c3,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I hope you know what'll happen...if you're too loud...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x127,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Yes, kinda..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c9,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Good. I'm glad you understand your predicament."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x127,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "(Wh-Wh-Wh-What should I do? I-I wonder if she's gonna do something to me...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x128,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "(I-I guess I have to talk her to lighten up the mood, so she'll be a bit less scary...!)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "U-Umm, you look very nice in Linca's outfit."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "(What in the world am I saying!?)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c4,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I guess, we do have the same face. If it looks good on her, it should look good on me, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c4,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "It is such a luxury, don't you think? She has five or six of the same outfit!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c9,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Don't you think it's unfair that she's the only one who gets this, while we don't have the money to buy clothes?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "(Whaaa‐! How am I supposed to answer a question like that?)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c5,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "So? Don't you think that's unfair?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Well...I heard she has spares because her clothes rip too easily..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "We were very close with her. We were always together, no matter what we were doing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x166,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "But then that woman appeared out of nowhere one day, and took her away..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "(Sh-She totally ignored my comment about the clothes!)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x16b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "It's Linca's fault, too. She's totally attached to that woman now... This is unforgivable, don'tcha think?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Oh, that's... I-I wonder, haha, heh..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c3,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, what do you think...? Between Marion and Linca, who's the bad one?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "(Another unanswerable question! What should I do? How can I answer...?)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Well, I  don't really know about the situation, but... Umm..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "I can't picture either one of them as \"bad\" people, so I'm sorry..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c4,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "...Hmm, I see. You're quite boring.<CR>You should at least try to play along."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Hyaaah! I'm so sorry!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c4,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "It's fine. It's not like I care about your opinion anyway."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "(Then don't ask me...!)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c4,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Putting that aside, I want you to give those two a message..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c4,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Will you tell them to bring what's most important to them to the ruin to the south?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c8,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "But just relaying that message isn't enough... You must accept responsibility for bringing them. Okay?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Y-Yes. I understand!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x19c,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "Good girl. I'm counting on you!<CR>See ya!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "(Whaaa‐! This doesn't look good! But first, I need to tell them about this.)"
        }
    ]
}